headline: 1 Incredible Reason to Buy This Value Stock Before Wall Street Catches On

headline: MP Materials Stock: Bull vs. Bear
summary: The Department of Defense and Apple deals are great news, but what happens next?  Trying to time the pullback in MP Materials stock is better left to the fortunetellers -- not smart investors.  Skyrocketing more than 275% since the start of the year (as of this writing), shares of MP Materials (NYSE: MP) have benefited from strong investor interest in rare earth metals and magnets.

headline: Could Apple Soon Lose Its Top Position in Warren Buffett's Portfolio?
summary: Apple remains the biggest position in Berkshire's portfolio.  By the end of 2025, Warren Buffett will no longer be the CEO of Berkshire Hathaway (NYSE: BRK.A)(NYSE: BRK.B).  Many investors are wondering what portfolio changes will be in store once Buffett departs and his lieutenants take full control over the business.
